### Carbon Report Month API 测试

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/carbonReportMonth
@token = your_token_here

### 1. 创建碳报告月报
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "collection_date": "2026-03-01 00:00:00",
  "turnover": 45000.50,
  "baseline": 36000.00,
  "energyConsumption": 8500.25,
  "carbonReduction": 9000.50
}

### 2. 更新碳报告月报
PUT {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": 1234567890
}

### 3. 删除碳报告月报
DELETE {{baseUrl}}?id=1234567890
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 根据ID查询碳报告月报
GET {{baseUrl}}?id=1234567890
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 分页查询碳报告月报
GET {{baseUrl}}s/page?pageNum=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=collection_date&sortOrder=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. 分页查询 - 带日期范围
GET {{baseUrl}}s/page?pageNum=1&pageSize=10&startDate=2026-01-01&endDate=2026-12-31&sortBy=collection_date&sortOrder=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
